license), ("Authorized  Users"), using  the RidgeRun Software  for one
Product  Application,  unless  otherwise  authorized  by  RidgeRun  in
writing for  a greater number  of Product Applications,  in accordance
with the terms hereof, only for  customer's benefit, and that no other
party shall have such use or  access to the RidgeRun Software, whether
or not such party is affiliated with customer.

 

